## 六、特殊效果

### 6.1 道法光晕
```css
/* 金色光晕效果 - 用于重要元素 */
.glow-gold {
    box-shadow: 
        0 0 20px rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.3),
        0 0 40px rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.2),
        0 0 60px rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.1);
}

.glow-gold::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -2px;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, 
        transparent 30%, 
        rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.3) 50%, 
        transparent 70%);
    border-radius: inherit;
    animation: shimmer 3s infinite;
}

@keyframes shimmer {
    0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
    100% { transform: translateX(100%); }
}
```

### 6.2 符文边框
```css
/* 用于特殊卡片边框 */
.rune-border {
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    background: 
        linear-gradient(rgba(26, 58, 42, 0.9), rgba(26, 58, 42, 0.9)) padding-box,
        linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a227, #5d9a7a, #8b2323, #c9a227) border-box;
    animation: borderRotate 4s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes borderRotate {
    0% { filter: hue-rotate(0deg); }
    100% { filter: hue-rotate(360deg); }
}
```

